   Accommodation for international student and more....
   [Where are you going ?]
   (BUTTON) Search

We help students to get connected to verified landlords and settle down in
France

   [choose.png]

1

Choose

   Select the place you are willing to rent and process the booking of
   your future accommodation
   [reserve.png]

2

Reserve

   The landlord has 48 hours to accept your booking request. Our support
   can be reached anytime
   [confirmation.png]

3

Confirmation

   Once accepted your payment method will automatically be charged. We
   will put you in contact with the landlord.
   [settle.png]

4

Settle

   Organize your arrival with the landlord or get some help by one of our
   locals in your future city
   How it works ?

LIVINFRANCE YOUR BUDDY IN FRANCE

   LivinFrance is an online platform designed for foreign and exchange
   students arriving in France.
   We work with local partners around France with one purpose : provide
   you a simple and secure process.
   We have a dedicated team to ensure you a safe and smooth experience
   while booking your accommodation.
   You can book your accommodation in 4 easy steps with LivinFrance. Our
   process not require any guarantor.
   We will assistant before, during and after your stay.
   About us

